# Source Insights Creation HTTP Request (Example)
# Use environment variables and keep secrets out of source control.

### Create Insights for Source
POST {{API_BASE_URL}}/api/sources/{{SOURCE_ID}}/insights
Accept: application/json, text/plain, */*
Authorization: Bearer {{API_PASSWORD}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "insight_type": "anki_multicard",
  "content": "Generate 5 vocabulary flashcards (front/back) for Dutch A1 level from this source",
  "tags": ["anki", "dutch", "a1"]
}

### Example env
# API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:5055
# API_PASSWORD=6596011
# SOURCE_ID=source:agl4023zwu6td14mjeff
